beq_correct.lemma_name: beq_correct  : forall x y, beq x y = true -> eq x y.

proof_steps: destruct x; destruct y; simpl in *.

ge_refl.lemma_name: ge_refl  : forall x y, eq x y -> ge x y.

ge_trans.lemma_name: ge_trans  : forall x y z, ge x y -> ge y z -> ge x z.

ge_lub_right.lemma_name: ge_lub_right  : forall x y, ge (lub x y) y.

lt_not_eq.lemma_name: lt_not_eq  : forall x y : t, lt x y -> ~ eq x y.

eq_trans.lemma_name: eq_trans  : forall x y z : t, eq x y -> eq y z -> eq x z.

proof_steps: intros x y z Hxy Hyz.

lessdef_vagree_list.lemma_name:
lessdef_vagree_list  :
  forall vl1 vl2, vagree_list vl1 vl2 nil -> Val.lessdef_list vl1 vl2.

vagree_lessdef_list.lemma_name:
vagree_lessdef_list  :
  forall vl1 vl2, Val.lessdef_list vl1 vl2 -> forall nvl, vagree_list vl1 vl2 nvl.

proof_steps: induction vl2 as [| v2 vl2' IHvl2'].

iagree_not.lemma_name:
iagree_not  :
  forall x y m, iagree x y m -> iagree (Int.not x) (Int.not y) m.

iagree_or.lemma_name:
iagree_or  :
  forall x y n m,
  iagree x y (Int.and m (Int.not n)) -> iagree (Int.or x n) (Int.or y n) m.

andimm_sound.lemma_name:
andimm_sound  :
  forall v w x n,
  vagree v w (andimm x n) ->
  vagree (Val.and v (Vint n)) (Val.and w (Vint n)) x.

orimm_sound.lemma_name:
orimm_sound  :
  forall v w x n,
  vagree v w (orimm x n) ->
  vagree (Val.or v (Vint n)) (Val.or w (Vint n)) x.

sub_sound.lemma_name:
sub_sound  :
  forall v1 w1 v2 w2 x,
  vagree v1 w1 (modarith x) -> vagree v2 w2 (modarith x) ->
  Archi.ptr64 = true ->
  vagree (Val.sub v1 v2) (Val.sub w1 w2) x.

proof_steps: apply eqmod_trans with (Int.unsigned i2 - Int.unsigned i).

modarith_idem.lemma_name: modarith_idem  : forall nv, modarith (modarith nv) = modarith nv.
